Survivor: Go! Paschal won the reward

We're just depleted energy-wise, you can feel it.

talking about missing home, moms, wives, boyfriends.
So it's getting really old. And I was good about it even up
until like I'm here three days ago.

My son is fine. He thinks it's great.

see what's happening with our mental stability.
